cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or data, please cite the manuscript below."
title: "Vegetation Greening and Climate Covariability in Subtropical Southern China (2001-2025)"
abstract: >-
  Data, code and figures supporting a seasonally resolved reassessment of
  vegetation greening across subtropical southern China using MODIS/061
  MOD13A3 NDVI and ERA5-Land climate reanalysis, combining GLS-AR(1) trends,
  Mann-Kendall/Theil-Sen detection, pixel-wise correlation, climate-adjusted
  regression, endpoint and split-period robustness testing, and Morlet
  wavelet coherence.
type: software
license: MIT
authors:
